Install Remastering Ubuntu 20.04 dengan Cubic terlebih dahulu

1. Install Cubic
	sudo apt-add-repository ppa:cubic-wizard/release
	sudo apt update
	sudo apt install cubic

2. Buat folder untuk Cubic
	mkdir -p /home/akitahm/BM-Nux

3. Buka Cubic, kemudian pilih folder Cubic yang telah dibuat sebelumnya, masukkan iso yang ingin di customize serta atur versi, nama, direktori, volume, id, release, dan disk name sesuai yang diinginkan.

4. Install aplikasi
	- Python 3.x
		apt install python3
    
	- Apache Server
		apt install apache2
    
	- Dia Diagram Editor
		apt install dia
    
	- Scilab
		apt install scilab
    
	- Multimedia Codecs
		apt install ubuntu-restricted-extras
    
	- VLC media player
		apt install vlc
    
	- Open Broadcaster Software (OBS)
		apt install obs-studio
    
	- Blender
		apt install blender
    
	- GimpShop
		apt install gimp
    
	- OpenOffice
		cd /opt
		wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/openofficeorg.mirror/files/4.1.7/binaries/en-US/Apache_OpenOffice_4.1.7_Linux_x86-64_install-deb_en-US.tar.gz/download
		tar -xvf download
		cd en-US/DEBS
		sudo dpkg -i *.deb
		cd desktop-integration
		dpkg -i *.deb	
		cd
    
	- Mendeley
		wget https://desktop-download.mendeley.com/download/apt/pool/main/m/mendeleydesktop_1.19.4-stable_amd64.deb
		dpkg -i mendeleydesktop_1.19.4-stable_amd64.deb
		apt -f install

  - Mengubah logo, wallpaper, dan tema
	  a. Ubah logo
      cd /usr/share/icons/hicolor/256x256/apps
      buka gambar yang ingin dijadikan logo, drag+copy ke terminal
      mv logobaru.png ubuntu-logo-icon.png
      ls
      cd
	  b. Ubah wallpaper
      cd /usr/share/backgrounds
      buka gambar yg ingin dijadikan wallpaper, drag+copy ke terminal
      mv wallpaperBaru.png warty-final-ubuntu.png
      ls
      cd
	  c. Ubah tema
		  apt install plymouth-themes

6. Save & Generate

7. Install file iso baru yang sudah dibuat
